overview: NXT 2.0's best and brightest Superstars converge on American Airlines Center in Dallas. Bron Breakker challenges Dolph Ziggler for the coveted NXT Championship. NXT Women's Champion Mandy Rose collides with Cora Jade, Io Shirai and Kay Lee Ray in a Fatal 4-Way Match. Carmelo Hayes puts his NXT North American Title on the line in a Ladder Match.
title: NXT Stand & Deliver 2022
